asciio (1.97.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Interactive ASCII diagram drawing tool
  * Supports both GUI (GTK3) and TUI interfaces
  * Vim-like keybindings for efficient editing
  * Export to ASCII text format
  * Unicode support for international characters
  * Customizable stencils and templates

